### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@categoryId = your-category-id-here
@recordId = your-record-id-here

### Get all income records
GET {{baseUrl}}/income-records

### Get income record by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/income-records/{{recordId}}

### Create income record
POST {{baseUrl}}/income-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "clientName": "John Doe",
  "unitPrice": 100.50,
  "unitCount": 5,
  "unitType": "HOURS",
  "notes": "Payment for consulting services",
  "recordedBy": "user-id-123"
}

### Update income record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/income-records/{{recordId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "clientName": "Jane Doe",
  "unitPrice": 150.00,
  "unitCount": 10,
  "unitType": "DAYS",
  "notes": "Updated payment details"
}

### Delete income record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/income-records/{{recordId}}
